Title: Slumming
Actors: Paulus Manker, August Diehl, Michael Ostrowski, Pia Hierzegger
Plot: Sebastian and Alex are two egocentric yuppies who stockpile underhanded up-skirt shots and bully others for their own amusement. On a night out they come across an inebriated man passed-out on a park bench and decide to prank him by smuggling him across the border.
